Package: milestones
Title: Milestone and bar-timeline graphics from table data
Version: 0.1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kim", "Bridges", , "kim.bridges@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Uses a table-oriented input design to specify the
    layout and graphic properties of milestone and bar-timeline
    graphics. These charts tie in nicely with presentation
    tables. These functions work inside the "ggplot2" universe.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://kim.quarto.pub/milestones--bar-timelines
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2
